metadata.description:
A video from the 2022 archives: Luiz reviews new types of real and simulated touch sensors to consider using with Monty.

00:00 Introduction
00:08 Touch Sensor Real and Simulated
00:41 DIGIT - Vision-Based Tactile Sensor
01:44 DIGIT - Sensor Output
03:07 DIGIT - Sensor Simulator
05:56 Questions
